[[div class="blockquote"]]

**###ff00ff|lesbian_gengar:##** you've really done it this time Peppa.
##purple|**PPS1337:**## What? What did I do?
**Starspark:** Don't play dumb. You gave Seshat to [*http://scp-int.wikidot.com/groups-of-interest-jp#pamwac PAMWAC] and look what they did!
##purple|**PPS1337:**## I thought it would be funny! I was getting bored with all the altruism.
##green|**bluntfiend:**## As they say it's all fun and games until someone gets hurt. Someone did.
##purple|**PPS1337:**## Look if anyone got hurt it was prolly kektagon's fault.
**kektagon:** Don't deflect blame on me! Nobody ever got hurt gaming.
##purple|**PPS1337:**## Idk maybe they did. I remember the [[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-3108 |nerfing gun]]] incident.
**###ff00ff|lesbian_gengar:##** pEPPA A COLLEGE KID BROKE THEIR NECK
