**Starspark:** Yeah it happened to my buddy eric.
**###ff00ff|lesbian_gengar:##**  this is not the time for debate, we've got eyes looking at us now that someone get hurt, and now the Foundation is gonna come knocking.
##purple|**PPS1337:**## What are we going to do?
##green|**bluntfiend:**## the real question is what you are doing to fix this.
